.TH SINGINE-PLATFORM 1 "2026-03-19" "singine 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
singine-platform \- generate platform blueprints and starter scaffolds for Singine, Collibra, Flowable, and OpenShift
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B singine platform blueprint
[\fB--title\fR \fITEXT\fR]
[\fB--output-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--json\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B singine platform blueprint
writes a concrete platform contract and starter scaffold for the broader
Singine stack. The blueprint aligns:
.IP \(bu 2
Docker and local CentOS or RHEL farm deployment
.IP \(bu 2
OpenShift and edge deployment shape
.IP \(bu 2
Node.js web shell
.IP \(bu 2
Python notebook-facing API
.IP \(bu 2
Spring Boot metadata adapter interfaces
.IP \(bu 2
Singine Clojure core orchestration
.IP \(bu 2
Flowable execution ordering
.IP \(bu 2
Collibra plain-text execution attributes
.PP
The blueprint is intentionally scaffold-first: it creates the file layout and
contracts, but it does not install npm packages or download external artifacts.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --title
Override the blueprint title.
.TP
.B --output-dir
Directory where the scaffold is written.
Defaults to
.IR /tmp/singine-platform-blueprint .
.TP
.B --json
Print the generated manifest as JSON instead of printing the Markdown path.
.SH GENERATED FILES
.IP \(bu 2
.I platform-blueprint.json
.IP \(bu 2
.I platform-blueprint.md
.IP \(bu 2
.I deploy/openshift-template.yaml
.IP \(bu 2
.I webapp/package.json
.IP \(bu 2
.I webapp/server.js
.IP \(bu 2
.I webapp/public/index.html
.IP \(bu 2
.I webapp/public/styles.css
.IP \(bu 2
.I python-api/service.py
.IP \(bu 2
.I spring-adapter/src/main/java/io/sindoc/singine/platform/MetadataProtocolAdapter.java
.SH COLLIBRA ALIGNMENT
The generated blueprint explicitly carries the three plain-text attribute
families used for governed execution:
.IP \(bu 2
.B Script Body
\(em workflow definition bodies
.IP \(bu 2
.B Source Code
\(em Groovy, Python, shell, and adapter source
.IP \(bu 2
.B Authorised Commands
\(em pipe-separated allow-lists for sanctioned execution
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
# Write the full scaffold.
singine platform blueprint

# Write to a named output directory and print the manifest.
singine platform blueprint \\
  --title "Singine Edge Flowable Platform Blueprint" \\
  --output-dir /tmp/singine-platform-blueprint \\
  --json
.fi
